---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy - Echo4Ever" description="Your memories, your rules. How Echo4Ever protects your privacy by design.">

  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 style="font-weight: 700;">Your privacy is built in â€” not bolted on</h1>
      <p>We designed Echo4Ever around one principle: your memories belong to you.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Private by Default -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="feature-detail feature-detail--with-image">
        <div class="feature-detail__image">
          <img src="/images/icon-private.svg" alt="Private by Default" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="feature-detail__content">
          <h2 style="font-weight: 700;">Private by Default</h2>
          <p>Every memory you create starts completely private, visible only to you. Sharing is always a conscious choice â€” never an accident. Nothing is ever shared without your explicit say-so.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- No Public Profiles -->
  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="feature-detail feature-detail--with-image feature-detail--reverse">
        <div class="feature-detail__image">
          <img src="/images/icon-family.svg" alt="No Public Profiles" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="feature-detail__content">
          <h2 style="font-weight: 700;">No Public Profiles</h2>
          <p>There are no public profiles. No social feeds. No algorithms deciding who sees your life. Your archive is yours and it stays that way.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- You Control Access -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="feature-detail feature-detail--with-image">
        <div class="feature-detail__image">
          <img src="/images/icon-access.svg" alt="You Control Access" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="feature-detail__content">
          <h2 style="font-weight: 700;">You Control Access</h2>
          <p>You decide who sees what and when. Family members can only ever see what you've specifically shared with them. Change your mind at any time. Nothing is permanent unless you want it to be.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Time-Locked Content -->
  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="feature-detail feature-detail--with-image feature-detail--reverse">
        <div class="feature-detail__image">
          <img src="/images/icon-timelock.svg" alt="Time-Locked Content" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="feature-detail__content">
          <h2 style="font-weight: 700;">Time-Locked Content</h2>
          <p>Time Capsules stay sealed until the date you set â€” even from you. They're your way of reaching into the future and being there for the moments that matter.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Your Legacy, Protected -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="feature-detail feature-detail--with-image">
        <div class="feature-detail__image">
          <img src="/images/icon-legacy.svg" alt="Your Legacy Protected" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="feature-detail__content">
          <h2 style="font-weight: 700;">Your Legacy, Protected</h2>
          <p>Appoint someone you trust as your Heritage Custodian. When the time comes, the memories you've chosen will be gently shared with the people you've named. Nothing more, nothing less. Exactly as you intended.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trust, Simplified -->
  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="feature-detail feature-detail--with-image feature-detail--reverse">
        <div class="feature-detail__image">
          <img src="/images/icon-vault.svg" alt="Trust Simplified" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="feature-detail__content">
          <h2 style="font-weight: 700;">Trust, Simplified</h2>
          <p>Your memories are locked away safely â€” like a vault that only you hold the key to. We can't see them. We don't sell them. We don't share them. Only the people you choose, at the times you choose, will ever have access.</p>
          <p><strong>That's not a feature. That's a promise.</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Three visibility levels -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 style="font-weight: 700;">Three levels of visibility</h2>
      <p class="text-secondary" style="margin: 0 auto 40px;">We don't believe in complicated settings or confusing permissions.</p>
      <div class="grid grid--3">
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="feature-icon"><img src="/images/icon-private.svg" alt="Private" class="feature-icon__img" /></div>
          <h3 style="font-weight: 700;">Private</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary">Only you can see it. No one else. Ever.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="feature-icon"><img src="/images/icon-family.svg" alt="Family" class="feature-icon__img" /></div>
          <h3 style="font-weight: 700;">Family</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary">Shared with the family members you've invited.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="feature-icon"><img src="/images/icon-legacy.svg" alt="Legacy" class="feature-icon__img" /></div>
          <h3 style="font-weight: 700;">Legacy</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary">Kept safe until your legacy is activated by your Heritage Custodian. The memories you've chosen are gently shared with the people you've named.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Legal Documents -->
  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 style="font-weight: 700;">Legal Documents</h2>
      <p class="text-secondary" style="margin: 0 auto 40px;">Read our full policies for complete details.</p>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 24px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="/Privacy%20Policy%20-Echo4ever.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn btn--primary">Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="/Terms%20of%20Service%20-%20Echo4ever.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn btn--primary">Terms of Service</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="font-weight: 700;">Your memories deserve better</h2>
      <p>Keep them somewhere private, secure and entirely under your control.</p>
      <a href="https://app.echo4ever.com/signup" class="btn btn--primary btn--large">Create Your Archive</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>

<style>
  .feature-detail {
    max-width: 100%;
    margin: 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .feature-detail__content {
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .feature-detail__content p {
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 24px);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .feature-detail h2 {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
</style>
